conflict zone. 
  The press centre the Karabakh Defence Army Staff told SNARK 
that on May 4 dawn Azerbaijani side, using the armoured 
hardware, tried to break through the Karabakh forces' positions 
at the eastern (Agdam) [parenthesis as received] sector of the 
front. According to the data received by this midday, the 
attacks of Azerbaijani troops were beaten off. The Azerbaijani 
side has considerable losses in man power. The Karabakh side 
has no losses. 
  Meanwhile, according to the same source, the intensive 
accumulation of Azerbaijani troops and hardware is observed in 
the north of Mardakert region of Karabakh. 

