<H3> <TI>   Current Status of Karabakh Situation Reviewed </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Current Status of Karabakh Situation Reviewed </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PM0205105994 Moscow IZVESTIYA in Russian 30 Apr 94 p 3 </F>
