<F P=100> INTERREGIONAL AFFAIRS </F>
<H3> <TI>   Shumeyko Urges Creation of CIS Peacekeeping Force </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Shumeyko Urges Creation of CIS Peacekeeping Force </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD0405173494 Moscow Russian Television Network in Russian 
1600 GMT 4 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0405173494 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow Russian Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [From the "Vesti" newscast] </F>
  [Text] Vladimir Shumeyko, chairman of the CIS 
Interparliamentary Assembly, told a POSTFAKTUM agency 
correspondent of the need to create a contingent of peacekeeping 
forces from CIS countries. In his opinion, the internal 
problems of the CIS members should be settled with the aid of 
this contingent. The Federation Council speaker is certain that 
it will be noted in the minutes of the Bishkek meeting that CIS 
parliamentarians are in favor of Commonwealth peacekeeping 
forces with a defined status and uniform. 

</TEXT>

