<F P=102>   LD0505080594 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 0130 GMT 
5 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0505080594 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow Mayak Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Boris Yeltsin has formed a national committee of the 
Russian Federation to prepare for paricipation in the world 
summit in the interests of social development. The Russian 
president's instruction notes that the national committee has 
been set up in connection with the UN General Assembly 
resolution which envisages the holding of a world meeting in 
Copenhagen in March 1995. Deputy Prime Minister Yuriy Yarov has 
been given the post of chairman of the committee. This was 
reported by the press service of the Russian Federation 
president. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

<DOC>
<DOCNO> FBIS4-61213 </DOCNO>
<HT>    "drsov087_b_94008" </HT>


<HEADER>
