<H3> <TI>   Yeltsin Issues Labor Protection Edict </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Yeltsin Issues Labor Protection Edict </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD0505053994 Moscow Radio Rossii Network in Russian 0200 GMT 
5 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0505053994 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow Radio Rossii Network </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Boris Yeltsin has issued an edict relating to state 
supervision and monitoring of the observance of legislation on 
labor and labor protection. The edict is aimed at ensuring 
guarantees of the constitutiional right of citizens to work in 
conditions corresponding to the requirements of safety and 
hygiene. 

</TEXT>

