<F P=100> CENTRAL ASIA </F>
<F P=101> Kyrgyzstan </F>
<H3> <TI>   Akayev Receives Japenese Fund Representatives </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Akayev Receives Japenese Fund Representatives </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD0405194194 Bishkek Kyrgyz Radio First Program Network in 
Kyrgyz 1605 GMT 4 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0405194194 </F>
<F P=104>  Bishkek Kyrgyz Radio First Program Network </F>
<F P=105>  Kyrgyz </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Askar Akayev received today a delegation of the 
Japanese Fund Sotokawa. The delegation is being led by Mr. 
Takaya, the director general of the fund's department for 
international affairs. Its goal is to contribute to the efforts 
of the UN organization in peace-making activities and support 
those who have suffered from natural disasters. 

</TEXT>

