<H3> <TI>   Supreme Soviet Chairman, Premier Begin Visit to Moldova </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Supreme Soviet Chairman, Premier Begin Visit to Moldova </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   WS0505115594 Minsk Radio Minsk Network in Belarusian 1000 
GMT 5 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> WS0505115594 </F>
<F P=104>  Minsk Radio Minsk Network </F>
<F P=105>  Belarusian </F>


